\p pamigumo yamativi okumusoro;
\v 14 ndichakwira kumusoro kwamakore, ndichazvienzanisa noWokumusoro-soro.'
\v 15 Kunyange zvakadaro uchaderedzwa kusvikira paSheori, kusvikira pakadzika pegomba.
\p
\v 16 "Vanokuona vachakucherekedza, vachakutarira, vachiti, `Ko uyu ndiye munhu aidederesa nyika, aizunungusa ushe;
\v 17 aishandura nyika ifanane nerenje, aiparadza maguta ayo, airamba kusunungura vasungwa vake vaende kumusha here?'
\p
\v 18 "Madzimambo ose amarudzi, iwo ose, anovata achikudzwa, mumwe nomumwe paimba yake.
\v 19 Asi iwe waraswa kure nobwiro hwako, sedavi rinonyangadza, wafukidzwa navakaurawa, vakabayiwa nomunondo, vanoburukira kumabwe egomba, somutumbi watsikwa netsoka.
\v 28 Haungavigwi pamwechete navo, nokuti wakaparadza nyika yako, vakauraya vanhu vako; vana vavakaipa havangarehwi nokusingaperi.
\v 21 Gadzirirai vana vake pavangaurawa nokuda kwokushata kwamadzibaba avo; varege kuzomuka, vagare nhaka yenyika, vazadze pasi pose namaguta."
\p
\v 22 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, "Ndichavamukira, ndichatorera Bhabhironi zita navakasara, navana, navana vavana, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 23 Ndichariita nzvimbo inogarwa nenhungu, uye madziva emvura; ndicharitsvaira nomutsvairo wokuparadza, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha wehondo."
\s Chirevo pamusoro pavaAsiria
\p
\v 24 Jehovha wehondo akapika, achiti, "Zvirokwazvo, sezvandakafunga, ndizvo zvichaitika; sezvandakarangarira, zvichamira saizvozvo.
\v 25 Kuti ndichavhuna muAsiria munyika yangu, ndichamutsika netsoka dzangu pamakomo angu; nenguva iyo joko rake richabva kwavari, nomutoro wake uchabva pamafudzi avo."
\v 26 Ndicho chirevo chakatemerwa nyika yose; ndirwo ruoko rwakatambanudzwa pamusoro pamarudzi ose.
\v 27 Nokuti Jehovha wehondo wakatema chirevo, ndiani angapindurazve? Ruoko rwake rwakatambanudzwa, ndiani angarudzosa.
\s Chirevo pamusoro pavaFirisitia
\p
\v 28 Negore rokufa kwamambo Ahazi chirevo ichi chakarehwa,
\p
\v 29 "Iwe nyika yeFirisitia, iwe nyika yose, usafara zvako nokuti shamhu yakanga yakurova yavhunika; nokuti pamudzi wenyoka pachabuda mvumbi, chibereko chayo chichava nyoka yomoto inoburuka.
\v 3 Â° Matangwe avarombo achadya, navanoshayiwa vachavata pasi vakafara; ndichauraya mudzi wako nenzara, vakasara vako vachaurawa.
\p
\v 31 "Chema, iwe suo; danidzira, iwe guta; wanyauka, iwe nyika yeFirisitia, iwe nyika yose; nokuti kurutivi rwokumusoro kunobva utsi, hapana anotiza pahondo dzake."
\v 32 Zvino nhume dzorudzi urwu vachadzipindurei? Kuti, "Jehovha akavamba Zioni, vanotambudzika navanhu vake vachavandiramo."
